---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-content">
    <div class="footer-section">
      <h4>MailCatcher NG</h4>
      <p>Beautiful SMTP server for email testing in development</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-section">
      <h4>Documentation</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/mailcatcher/install/">Installation</a></li>
        <li><a href="/mailcatcher/api/">REST API</a></li>
        <li><a href="/mailcatcher/claude/">Claude Integration</a></li>
        <li><a href="/mailcatcher/advanced/">Advanced</a></li>
        <li><a href="/mailcatcher/remote-access/">Remote Access</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-section">
      <h4>Community</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/spaquet/mailcatcher" target="_blank">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/spaquet/mailcatcher/issues" target="_blank">Issues</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/spaquet/mailcatcher/discussions" target="_blank">Discussions</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-section">
      <h4>Resources</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/spaquet/mailcatcher/blob/main/LICENSE" target="_blank">License</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/spaquet/mailcatcher/blob/main/README.md" target="_blank">README</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <p>&copy; {currentYear} MailCatcher NG. Licensed under MIT.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background-color: #1f2937;
    color: #d1d5db;
    padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .footer-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-section h4 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .footer-section p {
    color: #e5e7eb;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .footer-section li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .footer-section a {
    color: #e5e7eb;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .footer-section a:hover {
    color: #a7f3d0;
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-top: 1px solid #374151;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }
</style>
